========================================================================
Backgrounds

background-color: green;
opacity: 0.3; (=transparency)

background-image: url("paper.gif");

background-image: url("img_tree.png");
background-repeat: no-repeat;  (repeat-x; repeat-y;)
background-position: right top;

background-attachment: scroll; / fixed;
	-background image should scroll or be fixed
	

float: right; / right/ none / inherit
	-positioning and formatting content

////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
Flex box
======================

🔵️ flex-direction --> define main axis and the direction

flex-direction: row;		- row left to write
flex-direction: row-reverse;	- row right to left
flex-direction: column;		- column top to bottom
flex-direction: column-reverse;	- column bottom to top




